
@startuml
title OrangeHRM – OAuth2 Password Grant (Bearer) via Postman

actor User
participant Postman
participant "OrangeHRM OAuth" as OAuth
participant "OrangeHRM API" as API

User -> Postman : Run "OAuth – Issue Token"
Postman -> OAuth : POST /oauth/issueToken\nclient_id, client_secret, username, password, grant_type=password
OAuth --> Postman : { access_token, expires_in }
Postman -> Postman : set env.orangehrm_access_token
User -> Postman : Send API request
Postman -> API : GET /api/v1/employee/search\nAuthorization: Bearer <token>
API --> Postman : 200 OK (JSON)
Postman --> User : Show employees
@enduml
